::The Oblitercons/Scattershot/Punch/Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

All the Oblitercons except for Dark One (who's laying unconscious in the 
torture chambers) jump up at the transmission from Zergling, taking off 
toward the exit of the base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Still shivering in a corner from his encounter with 'ghosts', Scattershot 
recieves Zergling's message.

"Hear that?" he asks DeathStorms head, which naturally stays silent (dead 
heads don't ussually talk), "Bots to kill!"

With that, Scattershot jumps up, running off for the exit.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Reptilica and Bloodystrike look up from their game as they recieve the 
message.

"We'll patroll inside the base for now," Reptilica says, standing up. 
Bloodystrike nods, also getting to his feet.
